<TEXTAREA wrap=hard NAME="comment" ROWS="30" COLS="78" >政景＠鬼兜．E'ciさんは No.7019「PoS ROG1」で書きました。
>You say, 'I choose Rayne.'
>Thalik Silenthand says 'Rayne it shall be.  Take this book and read it.  
>When you are finished, hand it back to me and I shall summon the mighty 
>rogue Rayne to test you. 
>
>Thalik Silenthand から Tome of Shadows を受け取り、返します。
>
>Thalik Silenthand says 'Farewell. 
>Rayne says 'Rayne has come. 
>
>Rayne が現われ、Thalik Silenthand が消えます。
>
>You say, 'Hail Rayne'
>Rayne says 'Welcome, Xxxxxx .  I am apprentice Rayne.  Do you wish to test 
>your abilities? Or perhaps you would like to find out what I have to trade? 
>
>You say, 'What abilities?'
>Rayne says 'Great, let us waste no more time!  Do you wish to begin your 
>test of deception, stealth, or cunning? 
>
>You say, 'I  choose test of deception.'
>Rayne says 'Deception it is.  Proceed upward through the sky and return to 
>me the honied nectar, a bixie stinger from this plane, a lightning rod, and 
>a bloodsky sapphire for the test of deception and earn Thornstinger, dirk 
>of rampage. 
>
>You say, 'I  choose test of stealth.'
>Rayne says 'Stealth is a must.  Travel among the residents of the sky and 
>bring to me a pegasus statuette, a prismatic sphere, and a fine wool 
>cloak.  In return, the shimmering bracer of protection shall be yours. 
>
>You say, 'I  choose test of cunning.'
>Rayne says 'Cunning, the true source of all rogue power.  Plan and succeed 
>above us and return to me a bronze disc, a destule mask, and some red face 
>paint to complete the test of cunning.  The crystal mask shall be yours if 
>you do so. 
>
>You say, 'I would like to find out what you have to trade.'
>Rayne says 'Bartering is another important skill.  Sometimes finding 
>something that most consider junk can be useful to another for a whole 
>different reason.  Find me a Transparent Mask, Bracer of Protection or 
>Ebonsting and I will search out a much better upgrade for you.
